
# Cache geometry
@gRect Geometry rect
@gSphere Geometry sphere 1.0

# Cache materials
@mFloor Material matte (0.2 1.0  0.8 0.7 0.6 1.0)
@mRed   Material phong (0.2 2.0  1.0 0.3 0.3 1.0    2  1 1 1 1  32)
@mReflective Material reflective (0.2 0.5  1 1 1 1    0.15  1 1 1 1  100    0.75  1 1 1 1)


Camera
    pos 0 15 7
    lookat 0 2 0
    up 0.0 1.0 0.0
    type pinhole 
    params 1.0 2.0
        
    
    
Light ambient  (0.6   1 1 1    0.25)
Light point (0.5  1 1 1   0 10 -3  true)


@floor Renderable
    Transform 0 -2 0    0 0 0   1 1 1
    Geometry plane
    Material @mFloor
   
@mirror Renderable
    Transform 0 0 -5    0 90 0    1 4 4
    Geometry @gRect
    Material @mReflective
    
    
@sphere1 Renderable
    Transform 0 0 0   0 0 0   1 1 1
    Geometry @gSphere
    Material @mReflective
    
@sphere2 Renderable
    Transform 4 2 0   0 0 0   1 1 1
    Geometry @gSphere
    Material @mRed